VEvil.​Core.​FE.​FrontEndModuleInputSettings
public struct
VEvil.​Core.​FE.​FrontEndModuleInputSettings

Contain at which a AFrontEndModule should be enabled/disabled.

Set InputAction to null, the FrontEnd system will ignore Inputs.

Properties
InputAction
public InputAction InputAction {
get;
set
}

The InputAction to watch in order to enable/disable the AFrontEndModule.

EnableCondition
public InputActionPhase EnableCondition {
get;
set
}

The condition to enable the AFrontEndModule.

This value is ignored if InputAction is null!

DisableCondition
public InputActionPhase DisableCondition {
get;
set
}

The condition to disable the AFrontEndModule.

This value is ignored if InputAction is null!
